item.title: Portwarding
item.dc:creator: @mrprostats mrprostats
item.description:
@mrprostats wrote:

chaldopure:

i have tried everything when i gotta put the username and password i have tried the username being admin and pass: admin even user: pass: admin and user: admin pass:. mostly everything how do i get into it?

ima just jump right into this to not waste your time Smiley
click start, go to run then type “cmd”
then hit ok a black box comes up in it type “ipconfig”
then hit enter it should come up with all of your ip info.
ok now type in your default gateway into your web browser and hit enter if it
comes up with a user name and pass its ethier
username: admin/ password: admin
or username: admin/ password: password.
then click applications and games type in any name for the app.
the for the start and end points type “43594”
now the last box type the last 3 digits of your ip thats in your ip config.
in this case mine is 108 click enable and save then your done Smiley!
sorry if its confusing im in a rush here is a video to shortin things up Smiley
http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GsskvUnYOgw
please wait for youtube to review.
